Trinity::

She took a few steps closer to the male Hawk bot. "Hi. I'm Trinity. 
What' your name? And sure, we can be friends." She smiled and put a 
kitten paw on the bot's leg. She looked up at him, "So you want to be 
friends, huh, do you?" She giggled and pranced around the bot, waving 
her little kitten tail, and holding her head up.
